get-actor-machine-identifier
====================

A cross-platform JavaScript library for generating unique machine identifiers.

## Installation

```bash
npm install get-actor-machine-identifier
```

## Usage

### Node.js

```javascript
import { getActorMachineIdentifier } from 'get-actor-machine-identifier';
const identifier = await getActorMachineIdentifier();
```

### Browser

```javascript
import { getActorMachineIdentifier } from './get-actor-machine-identifier.js';
const identifier = await getActorMachineIdentifier();
```

## Output Format

3-6-9 base36 format: `xxx-xxxxxx-xxxxxxxxx`
- First 3 chars: Random component
- Next 6 chars: Machine-based component
- Last 9 chars: GUID-based component

## Requirements

- Node.js 18+ or modern browser with Web Crypto API
- ESM modules only

